data.title: International Bank of Yemen
data.meta_description: International Bank of Yemen was established in 1979. Subsequently, the bank became on top of the national banks that emerged after the revolution in September 26, 1962. During the forty years of its establishment, the bank worked sincerely to build a national force of healthy capital capable of bringing the Republic of Yemen into the heart of the time and its spirit of civilization and development.
